com.iha.emulator.models.value.implemented

Class OnOffActuatorValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iha.emulator.models.value.AbstractValue<java.lang.Boolean>
      • com.iha.emulator.models.value.implemented.OnOffActuatorValue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasBooleanRandom, HasGenerator, Value<java.lang.Boolean>

    public class OnOffActuatorValue
extends AbstractValue<java.lang.Boolean>
implements HasBooleanRandom
    Implementation of Value interface, extending AbstractValue representing On/Off actuator. Uses Boolean as value data type. Provides methods for storing, generating and saving value. For generating new values uses Boolean random generator.
    Author:
    Filip Sutovsky
